### Создать чат
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/v1/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "chatName": "Hello chat",
  "usersDetails": [
    {
      "username": "Apkawa",
      "encryptedSymmetricKey": "some_key1"
    },
    {
      "username": "test_user2",
      "encryptedSymmetricKey": "some_key2"
    },
    {
      "username": "test_user3",
      "encryptedSymmetricKey": "some_key3"
    }
  ]
}

###
#{
#  "code": 201,
#  "message": "Created",
#  "data": 50,
#  "timestamp": "2026-01-07T08:38:35.275153945"
#}


### Получить информацию о чате по {{id}} // лучше использовать GET /api/v1/chat/{{chatId}}/message
GET http://{{host}}:{{port}}/api/v1/chat/{{chatId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

